product_list.title: All-new Blink Weather Resistant 13ft Power Adapter for Blink Mini 2 and Blink Outdoor 4 (White)
description: Weather Resistant Power Adapter enables Blink Mini 2 for outdoor use and provides nonstop power for Blink Outdoor 4 (4th Gen) camera.
Do more with Blink — Compatible with USB-C enabled Blink devices, including Mini 2 and Outdoor 4.
Peace of mind, rain or shine — Weather resistant for trusted outdoor usage.
Includes one 13ft power adapter. Requires access to a standard outlet.
